'''索引大师'''（{{lang-en|IndexMaster}}<ref>{{cite book|title=Market Intelligence Resources 2008|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=IsVBYQfhH90C&pg=PT93|publisher=Marcus P.  Zillman|pages=93–|id=GGKEY:UNUJ8STKHC9}}</ref>）曾是一个[[美国|美国]][[法律|法律]][[研究|研究]][[数据库|数据库]]<ref>{{cite book|title=Legal Information Alert|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Css6AQAAIAAJ|year=1999|publisher=U.S. Law Information Alert, Incorporated|pages=7–}}</ref>，网站[[域名|域名]]IndexMaster.com<ref name="Ambrogi2004">{{cite book|author=Robert J. Ambrogi|title=The Essential Guide to the Best (and Worst) Legal Sites on the Web|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Y4oETB8_EbIC&pg=PA391|year=2004|publisher=ALM Publishing|isbn=978-1-58852-117-0|pages=391–}}</ref>注册于1996年12月19日<ref>{{cite web | url=https://whois.domaintools.com/indexmaster.com| title=Whois Record for IndexMaster.com|work=[[WHOIS|WHOIS]]|accessdate=2020-07-13}}</ref>，1998年开始运行<ref name="Olson1999">{{cite book|author=Kent C. Olson|title=Legal Information: How to Find It, how to Use it|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=BP5C6os40ToC&pg=PA73|year=1999|publisher=ABC-CLIO|isbn=978-0-89774-963-3|pages=73–}}</ref>，隶属于[[索引大师公司|索引大师公司]]（IndexMaster, Inc.）。

该网站允许[[用户|用户]]查找和预览法律出版物。检索结果允许研究者[[在线|在线]]查看[[目录|目录]]和[[索引|索引]]<ref name="caba">{{cite web|url=http://calbar.ca.gov/calbar/2cbj/98nov/newprod.htm |title=Internet research database shows actual contents |accessdate=2020-07-13|url-status=|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060925090328/http://www.calbar.ca.gov/calbar/2cbj/98nov/newprod.htm |archivedate=2006-09-25}}</ref>。该网站曾获得[[美国法律图书馆学会|美国法律图书馆学会]]（American Association of Law Libraries）<ref name="张慧铢林呈潢2019">{{cite book|author1=张慧铢|author2=林呈潢|author3=邱子恒|coauthors=黄元鹤|title=图书信息服务机构管理|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=5NDlDwAAQBAJ&pg=PA307|date=2019年12月20日|publisher=AinoscoPress|isbn=978-986-437-173-0|pages=307–}}</ref>2000年度最佳新产品奖<ref name="aall">{{cite web |url=http://www.aallnet.org/press/press000707np.asp |title=IndexMaster Receives 2000 AALL Best New Product Award |date=2000-07-07 |}}</ref>。目前，该网站已不再活跃，域名正在出售中<ref>{{cite news|url=http://indexmaster.com/|title=IndexMaster.com is for sale||publisher=IndexMaster.com|accessdate=2020-07-13}}</ref>。

